text: Valle Alto is: * Valle Alto (Monterrey) - an exclusive suburb within the city of Monterrey in Mexico * Valle Alto (La Paz) - name of the main valley of La Paz, Bolivia * Valle Alto (Cochabamba) - name of a region in the Cochabamba Department, Bolivia * Valle Alto (Hermigua) - name of the first settlement of Hermigua on La Gomera, Canary Islands
title: Valle Alto
